song.title: Leeroy Jenkins Fun Times Mix
song.info:
Leeroy Jenkins is legendary paladin, known from World of Warcraft. He bacame famous, because of movie from Upper Blackrock Spire instance, where he wiped out entire raid with crazy shout "Let's do this... Leeerroooooooyyyyy Jeeeeeennkkiiiiinnnnssss!!!!", charging in and pulling +-100 dragons.
Youtube for it;)
